OL,3,CJohn McGuinness: TT is 'too special to
OL,4,Clet go of' after 30 years
OL,6,FMorecambe's John McGuinness says the
OL,7,FIsle of Man TT is "too special to let
OL,8,Fgo of" as he prepares to take on the
OL,9,FMountain Course for his 30th year.
OL,11,FThe 54-year-old started his road
OL,12,Fracing career in 1996, but his love
OL,13,Ffor the TT began from an early age.
OL,15,FMcGuinness often recalls skipping
OL,16,Fschool aged 11 to jump on the ferry
OL,17,Fover to the island to witness the
OL,18,Fworld-famous road races.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
