CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779210358
OL,3,CJohn McGuinness: TT is 'too special to
OL,4,Clet go of' after 30 years
OL,6,FThirty years on, and the legendary
OL,7,Frider is preparing to return to the
OL,8,F37.73 Mountain Course with the same
OL,9,Flevel of excitement.
OL,11,F"I'm in a really really happy place -
OL,12,FI'm not feeling the pressure - I
OL,13,Falways wanted to win when I was at the
OL,14,Ftop of my game, but now I'm just happy
OL,15,Fbeing out on the track, enjoying what
OL,16,FI'm doing, being part of it, and just
OL,17,Fbeing safe."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779210358
OL,3,CJohn McGuinness: TT is 'too special to
OL,4,Clet go of' after 30 years
OL,6,FWhen asked if he felt like it had been
OL,7,F30 years since his first race,
OL,8,FMcGuinness said: "Not really. I
OL,9,Fremember coming off that ferry just
OL,10,Fover there in '96 knowing a little bit
OL,11,Fabout it, but not really understanding
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,F"It seems sort of a lifetime ago, but
OL,15,Falso sort of not."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779210358
OL,3,CJohn McGuinness: TT is 'too special to
OL,4,Clet go of' after 30 years
OL,6,FAs one of the most senior riders,
OL,7,FMcGuinness is often asked when he
OL,8,Fplans to hang his boots up - a
OL,9,Fquestion he's not fond of being asked
OL,10,F- but one he always knows how to
OL,11,Fanswer.
OL,13,F"I thought the decision would have
OL,14,Fbeen made for me", he said.
OL,16,F"I get on my bike, I put the helmet
OL,17,Fon, I go down Bray Hill, I go as fast
OL,18,FI can, I cross the line and I'm 6th
OL,19,Fand I think I'm still going alright
OL,20,Fhere!
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779210358
OL,3,CJohn McGuinness: TT is 'too special to
OL,4,Clet go of' after 30 years
OL,6,F"I feel like I'm riding in a safe
OL,7,Fzone, I don't feel like I'm coming out
OL,8,Fthat where I'd be feeling vulnerable.
OL,10,F"I don't want retirement to enter my
OL,11,Fhead because I've still got to do the
OL,12,Fsame thing - I've still got to prepare
OL,13,Fthe same way, I've still got to do the
OL,14,Ftesting the same way, I've still got
OL,15,Fto completely focus on the race.
OL,17,F"There's no point going 'this is going
OL,18,Fto be my last one', and take your eye
OL,19,Foff the ball, because that's the one
OL,20,Fthat will catch you out.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779210358
OL,3,CJohn McGuinness: TT is 'too special to
OL,4,Clet go of' after 30 years
OL,6,F"So at the minute it's focus focus
OL,7,Ffocus, push push push, ride ride ride,
OL,8,Fand then when we cross the line in the
OL,9,FSenior we'll have a look in the mirror
OL,10,Fand go 'do we wanna carry on doing
OL,11,Fthis?' - but I can't answer that until
OL,12,FI've crossed the line."
OL,14,FAlongside McGuinness' achievements,
OL,15,Fthis year will mark the first time
OL,16,FHollywood will be present at the
OL,17,Fracing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
