PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779210358
OL,3,CJohn McGuinness: TT is 'too special to
OL,4,Clet go of' after 30 years
OL,6,FA feature film, titled 'Isle of Man',
OL,7,Ffeatures Hollywood star Channing
OL,8,FTatum, while Brad Pitt will act as a
OL,9,Fproducer.
OL,11,FSpeaking about how the TT is going
OL,12,Fbeyond the racing, McGuinness said: "I
OL,13,Fspeak to Channing a little bit and
OL,14,Fhave a little bit of a chat with him,
OL,15,Fand he just loves it - loves the bikes
OL,16,F- I think it's fantastic.
OL,18,F"It's a big production It's a big
OL,19,FHollywood thing. I know some of the
OL,20,Fguys who are involved in it and, you
OL,21,Fknow, let's hope it's a success."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
